reviews.comment: Didn't follow the brief provided the first time. Then did an okay job on the re-write. It says SEO, but she provides no SEO description or titles to help with that or ask you for relevant keywords (I had to provide those) on the blogs that were written. I had to ChatGPT the SEO titles and description that were relevant  myself after the work was done. I went ahead and just approved it and fixed the things myself.

I have used numerous sellers in the last 8 months, I can prove in a court of law, beyond a reasonable doubt, that her displayed expertise is not only factual but understates her the value she adds by writing an incredibly wonderful landing page. Words currently escape me but my internal feelings after reading her deliverable have me feeling extremely filled with joy. Ms. Mongiardo deserves the highest accolades of Fiverr needs to hear to have her stays as high as you offer. You will not find better copywriting skills. I have never done business or chatted etc, and had a few back and forths..3 or so prior to the deliverable. To Fiverr: please look at her work!!

I was stunned by the service by Victoria! It went far beyond my expectations. It was my first time working with a content writer and originally I had no idea how it was like. I instantly chose her after looking at her profile and reviews, and I was RIGHT! 

Victoria reviewed all the contents on my website that I am working on. I am not a native speaker and I wanted her to polish sentences that I wrote. The amazing thing is that she kept the essence of what I want to say, but changed sentences to make it sound better and professional. Thank you so much!!!

Wow!! Victoria was able to take my mediocre marketing e-book and turn it into a really good e-book in only a few hours. Delivered a document with tracked changes so I could see exactly what she changed. Made reviewing the document super easy. Next time, I'll go straight to her and book another gig...

This was my second job with Victoria. Very professional. Delivered & responded on every request quickly.

I can highly recommend the AI review service.

I'll definetely do another blog post review. I already have a new post idea "Mastering Strategic Thinking: A Path to Professional Excellence". Probably doing it next Month.

But currently focusing on other topics like adding a comment section to my blog and smaller design improvments.
Thank you for sharing your valuable feedback. Please accept my vehement protestations of gratitude. Happy to help if you need anything.
